04:47.057 --> 04:50.491
(normal voice)
HI, EVERYBODY.

04:50.491 --> 04:51.662
AND KENNY.

04:51.662 --> 04:53.424
BRENDA, LISTEN.

04:53.424 --> 04:54.565
